{
  "texts": [
    "Our design rationale is based on the design guidelines proposed by Chuang et al. [18].",
    "We reuse their definitions of Model Alignment, Progressive Disclosure, and Unit of Analysis when describing our design rationale.",
    "We first identify common analysis tasks from previous works.",
    "Then, we derive our design considerations (DC) from the analysis tasks.",
    "We take the DCs into account during the data preparation and visualization design process in Section IV."
  ]
}